Chicago R User Group (CRUG)

  • Welcome new and current useRs to the Ath meetup of the year!
  • We are The Chicago R User Group launched (on Meetup) in 2010!
  • Now reached 3,700 members, one of largest groups in world!
  • We have an R package, RUGTools!
  • We even have a R Shiny app, CRUG Attendance App!
